<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <img src="~/img/LC_logo_sm.jpg" class="img-responsive" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
        <h2>Welcome to 'LocalCord'</h2>
        <p>LocalCord, India’s first service platform website, which helps you connect to the service experts near your locality which we call your cord. The service experts or providers and the consumers like you are connected to the cord near you. Each cord is having a local board in which the customer places the needs 
            and the service eperts picks up the leads. Our service experts or vendors are constantly monitoring any requirements
            and needs being posted on the local board. 
            </p>
        <p>Apart from posting the service needs you can use the board to post the current trends in your locality.The board is same as the facebook wall except it is open to all the users of the locality or cord. The local attractive deals and the referal coupons can be posted
        here and the platform helps you to let the users use your referal code thus benefitting you.</p>
    </div>
</div>
